    <main aria-label="About Glenn Stearns" class="view">
        <div class="view__anchor" id="main"></div>
        <div class="view__in">
            <div class="group group--speaker">
                <div class="group__item group__item--speaker">
                    <div class="copy copy--speaker">
                        <h2>GLENN STEARNS</h2>
                        <h3>Star of Discovery's Undercover Billionaire </h3>
                        <p>
                        	<strong>BUSINESS</strong>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                        	<strong>&#8220;Billionaire Secrets of Success&#8221;</strong>
                        </p>
                        <p>An inspirational leader, Glenn Stearns is best-known as the <strong>star of Discovery's breakout show, Undercover Billionaire</strong>. With just $100, a cell phone and a pickup truck, this real-life American business mogul set out to build a million dollar business from scratch in just 90 days &ndash; to prove <strong>the American Dream is still alive-and-well</strong> for those willing to work hard, take risks and go for it.</p>

                        <p>Stearns was born to alcoholic parents, dyslexic, failed 4th grade, fathered a child at the age of 14 and graduated high school in the bottom ten percent of his class. Despite his challenges growing up, and inspired by stories of people who took risks and achieved their grandest ambitions, Stearns went to college and eventually <strong>built a billion dollar business</strong>. His passion now is teaching others how to overcome obstacles and <strong>achieve</strong> their <strong>greatest potential</strong>.</p>

                        <p>During Glenn's session, he'll show you how to use adversity as a <strong>springboard to success</strong>. He'll show you how to overcome any obstacle that stands in the way of your dream and how hope, hard work, and a good idea can break you free from hardship, overcome challenges and help you <strong>live the life of your dreams</strong>. You'll learn:</p>

                        <ul class="copy__list">
                        	<li>How to <strong>Overcome Adversity</strong> and Attract Success</li>
                        	<li>How to Manage, <strong>Lead & Succeed</strong> in Business and in Life</li>
                        	<li>Get Motivated to Do Better, Be Better, & <strong>Achieve More</strong> in Life</li>
                        	<li>Secrets to <strong>Financial Success</strong></li>
                        	<li>How to <strong>Create Your Own Destiny</strong></li>
                        	<li>Learn How to Adapt, Survive and <strong>Thrive in any Economy</strong></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="group__item group__item--speaker-img">
                    <div class="arp arp--fill" style="--arp:374/419;max-width:374px">
                        <img src="/images/glenn-stearns.jpg" alt="Glenn Stearns">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

